   "source": [
    "# 🏎️ F1 Strategy Analyzer\n",
    "### Powered by FastF1 — Post-Race Analysis & Strategy Simulation\n",
    "\n",
    "**Project:** F1 Race Strategy Analyzer  \n",
    "**Data Source:** FastF1 (official F1 telemetry API)  \n",
    "**Author:** *(Dhanush C)*  \n",
    "**GitHub:** *(https://github.com/dhanushc13/f1-strategy-analyzer)*  \n",
    "\n",
    "---\n",
    "\n",
    "## What This Notebook Does\n",
    "1. **Fetches real F1 lap data** using FastF1 (lap times, tyre compounds, pit stops, sector splits)\n",
    "2. **Visualizes the Monaco GP 2023** circuit with heatmaps (speed zones, tyre stress, sector splits)\n",
    "3. **Plots tyre strategy** for all drivers\n",
    "4. **Tracks position changes** lap-by-lap\n",
    "5. **Simulates alternate pit strategies** — What if Hamilton pitted lap 25 instead of 32?\n",
    "\n",
    "---"
   ]
  },
