    "---\n",
    "## 📊 Section 3 — Sector Performance Comparison\n",
    "Compare all 5 drivers across S1, S2, S3 — where time is won and lost."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 9,
   "id": "6d3603f1",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "image/png": "",
